<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-1035] Add message-send-max-retries and retry-backoff-ms options to console producer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1035</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s possible for console producer to give up too soon if it can&apos;t find a leader of a topic. Increasing message-send-max-retries would resolve this but.  Console producer doesn&apos;t provide options to set message-send-max-retries and retry-backoff-ms. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12666154">KAFKA-1035</key>
