                            <comment id="13753772" author="erajasekar" created="Thu, 29 Aug 2013 16:12:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch for fixing this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13753773" author="erajasekar" created="Thu, 29 Aug 2013 16:13:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;See attachment for patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12600604/console_producer_add_options.patch&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12600604/console_producer_add_options.patch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13754254" author="guozhang" created="Fri, 30 Aug 2013 00:42:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch. One minor comment:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you modify the description of message-send-max-retries:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&quot;The leader may be unavailable transiently, which can fail the sending of a message. This property specifies the number of retries when such failures occur&quot;?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. Brokers can fail receiving the message for multiple reasons, and being unavailable transiently is just one of them.&lt;br/&gt;
2. This properties specifies the number of retires before the producer give up and drop this message.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13754918" author="erajasekar" created="Fri, 30 Aug 2013 17:20:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sure. do you want me to change description as &lt;br/&gt;
&quot;Brokers can fail receiving the message for multiple reasons, and being unavailable transiently is just one of them.This properties specifies the number of retires before the producer give up and drop this message.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13754955" author="guozhang" created="Fri, 30 Aug 2013 17:56:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;That is fine.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13755130" author="erajasekar" created="Fri, 30 Aug 2013 20:56:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch with modified description. Please review.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13755553" author="guozhang" created="Sat, 31 Aug 2013 16:52:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks good to me. +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13755561" author="erajasekar" created="Sat, 31 Aug 2013 17:44:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, So could you apply patch and commit changes to repo.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Raja.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13758616" author="guozhang" created="Thu, 5 Sep 2013 01:03:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry but I am not one of the committers.. Can someone (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=junrao&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;junrao&quot;&gt;junrao&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=nehanarkhede&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;nehanarkhede&quot;&gt;nehanarkhede&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jjkoshy&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jjkoshy&quot;&gt;jjkoshy&lt;/a&gt;) review/commit it?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
